<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Consola | <%= displayTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #050505; --card: #0f0f0f; --blue: #007bff; --green: #28a745; --red: #dc3545; --yellow: #ffc107; }
        body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: white; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        
        .header-server { padding: 20px 40px; background: var(--card); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        .server-info { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .status-badge { padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; background: var(--yellow); color: black; }
        
        /* Pestañas estilo Pterodactyl */
        .nav-tabs { display: flex; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .nav-tab { padding: 10px 20px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .nav-tab:hover, .nav-tab.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: white; }
        .nav-tab.active { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue); border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }

        .container { padding: 20px 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }

        /* Consola */
        .console-box { background: #000; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #222; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 450px; }
        .console-output { flex-grow: 1; padding: 15px; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-y: auto; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.5; }
        .console-input { background: #111; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #222; padding: 12px; color: white; outline: none; font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; }

        /* Controles y Stats */
        .controls { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .btn-ctrl { flex: 1; padding: 12px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; color: white; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; }
        .btn-start { background: var(--green); }
        .btn-restart { background: #444; }
        .btn-stop { background: var(--red); }

        .stat-card { background: var(--card); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .stat-icon { width: 45px; height: 45px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; }
        .stat-val { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: gray; text-transform: uppercase; }

        .node-info { background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 13px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header-server">
        <div class="server-info">
            <h1 style="margin:0;"><%= serverName %></h1>
            <span class="status-badge" id="status">Starting</span>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-tabs">
            <a href="#" class="nav-tab active"><i class="fas fa-terminal"></i> Console</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-tab"><i class="fas fa-file-code"></i> Files</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-tab"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> Startup</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-tab"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i> Backups</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-tab"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Settings</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-side">
            <div class="controls">
                <button class="btn-ctrl btn-start"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> START</button>
                <button class="btn-ctrl btn-restart"><i class="fas fa-redo"></i> RESTART</button>
                <button class="btn-ctrl btn-stop"><i class="fas fa-stop"></i> STOP</button>
            </div>

            <div class="node-info">
                <strong>NODO:</strong> AMD Ryzen™ 9 5950X, 16c/32t @3.40GHz, 128 GB...
            </div>

            <div class="console-box">
                <div class="console-output" id="console">
                    <span style="color: #ff5f5f;">[YotsuDactyl]</span> Inicializando vinculación para servidor...<br>
                    <span style="color: #28a745;">[LISTO]</span> Módulos cargados correctamente.<br>
                    <span style="color: #007bff;">[DOCKER]</span> Creando contenedor aislado...
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="console-input" placeholder="Type a command...">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="right-side">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="stat-label">CPU Usage</div>
                    <div class="stat-val">0.01% <span style="font-weight: normal; color: gray; font-size: 14px;">/ 130%</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Memory Usage</div>
                    <div class="stat-val">157 MiB <span style="font-weight: normal; color: gray; font-size: 14px;">/ 1 GiB</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-memory"></i></div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Disk Usage</div>
                    <div class="stat-val">186 MiB <span style="font-weight: normal; color: gray; font-size: 14px;">/ 4 GiB</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-save"></i></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">
        YotsuDactyl &copy; 2026 - Todos los derechos reservados.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>